# {{projectName}}

A conservation data dashboard built with [Uniweb](https://github.com/uniweb/cli) — a component web platform that separates content from code.

This template demonstrates **dynamic data fetching** — live API data with loading states, transforms, and the portable data pattern.

## What This Template Shows

- **Live API data** — Weather, blog posts, wildlife sightings, research papers, occurrence records
- **Loading states** — Custom skeleton UIs per section while data arrives
- **Data transforms** — Extracting nested data from API response envelopes (`results`, `message.items`, `current`)
- **Portable data pattern** — Site controls which APIs are called; foundation controls how data renders
- **Static data contrast** — Local JSON for video gallery (`prerender: true`)

